#: ../../library/tkinter.messagebox.rst:118
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Ask a question. Shows buttons :data:`YES`, :data:`NO` and :data:`CANCEL`. "
"Return ``True`` if the answer is yes, ``None`` if cancelled, and ``False`` "
